name: MyTrain
0:
”Alexa, ask my train for train 422”
”Alexa, ask my train what is the status of train 420”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my train
des:
This skill helps you to keep track of SEPTA train's status to see if it is late or where it is heading to. It uses real-time data from SEPTA API and analyzes it to give you the information you want.

This skill only uses SEPTA API and is not sponsored by SEPTA.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
